<item>
            <title>[LU-9240] Can the ldiskfs support Linux kernel 4.1.38+?</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-9240</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;I am studying the Lustre File System and need re-build the 2.9 Lustre with Linux Kernel 4.1.38. &lt;br/&gt;
But, the ldiskfs module has so many patches for ext3/ext4 only on Linux kernel 3.12 or earlier. Can the ldiskfs support Linux kernel 4.1.38 or later versions?&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment>Linux kernel 4.1.38+</environment>
        <key id="44936">LU-9240</key>
            <summary>Can the ldiskfs support Linux kernel 4.1.38+?</summary>
